OL,3,CTyne Tunnel tolls rise today ` what do
OL,4,Cdrivers need to know?
OL,6,FThe cost of using the Tyne Tunnel has
OL,7,Fincreased, with drivers now paying
OL,8,Fmore for each journey.
OL,10,FFrom 1 May 2026, the price has risen
OL,11,Fby 10p for cars and vans, taking the
OL,12,Fcharge to #2.60 per journey. Prices
OL,13,Fhave also increased for heavier
OL,14,Fvehicles.
OL,16,FIn February 2026, the North East
OL,17,FCombined Authority confirmed the new
OL,18,Frates, with Class 2 vehicles now
OL,19,Fpaying #2.60, and Class 3 vehicles
OL,20,F#5.20.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
