OL,3,CTyne Tunnel tolls rise today ` what do
OL,4,Cdrivers need to know?
OL,6,FPre-paid account holders will continue
OL,7,Fto receive a 10% discount, reducing
OL,8,Fcharges to #2.34 for Class 2 vehicles,
OL,9,Fand #4.68 for Class 3 vehicles.
OL,11,FTT2, the operating company for the
OL,12,Ftunnel, has said: "The Tyne Tunnels
OL,13,Fare an integral piece of the North
OL,14,FEast's road network and are privately
OL,15,Foperated and maintained roads.
OL,17,F"The construction of the second Tyne
OL,18,FTunnel, as well as the 24/7 operation
OL,19,Fand maintenance of both tunnels are
OL,20,Ffunded solely by tolls and do not
OL,21,Freceive public funding.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
