OL,3,CTyne Tunnel tolls rise today ` what do
OL,4,Cdrivers need to know?
OL,6,F"Toll changes are applied by the North
OL,7,FEast Combined Authority and are
OL,8,Fnecessary to cover the running and
OL,9,Fmaintenance costs of the tunnels and
OL,10,Frepay the costs of the construction of
OL,11,Fthe second Tyne Tunnel, in-line with
OL,12,Finflation."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
